      "Guaranteed response times with escalation paths for critical issues.",
    img_src:"https://res.cloudinary.com/daog6scxm/image/upload/e_grayscale/v1778147323/icons/priority_lmbvj0.png",
    img_format: "svg" as ImageInputFormat
  },
]


